ther, these make Bangaluru an ideal starting point for exploring South India\u2019s scientific and cultural treasures.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Weather<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Weather in Bangaluru is generally pleasant. Please click<a href=\"https:\/\/weather.com\/en-IN\/weather\/today\/l\/INXX0012:1:IN\">&nbsp;<\/a><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/weather.com\/en-IN\/weather\/today\/l\/INXX0012:1:IN\">here<\/a>&nbsp;<\/span>for details.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><br><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Visitor Guidelines For International participants The first batch of VISA clearance letters has been shared with the concerned participants. We are expecting the second batch of VISA clearance letters soon. While submitting for the e-conference VISA , you might require the local contact\/ organiser&#8217;s information. C M ChandrashekarDepartment of Electronic Systems EngineeringCV Raman Road, Indian [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_et_pb_use_builder":"off","_et_pb_old_content":"","_et_gb_content_width":"","footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-30856","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/tqc-conference.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/30856","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/tqc-conference.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/tqc-conference.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tqc-conference.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tqc-conference.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=30856"}],"version-history":[{"count":31,"href":"https:\/\/tqc-conference.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/30856\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":31540,"href":"https:\/\/tqc-conference.org